that. The company is one of the most hyped AI plays on the market and has greatly rewarded long-term investors. I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4663606-palantir-stock-a-lot-to-love-here\">initiated coverage</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426101020/image_1426101020.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742056-palantir-technologies-taking-profits-makes-sense-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:23:34"}, {"id": "4742055", "title": "BNY Mellon California AMT-Free Municipal Bond Fund, Inc. Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Selective focus of dollar notes and red tag written with MUNICIPAL BONDS on white wooden background.\" data-id=\"1300347507\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3881px\" height=\"2595px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1300347507/image_1300347507.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw 